### Create an enquiry
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "channel": "WhatsApp",
  "customer_name": "Ritika Sharma",
  "message": "I want to book a demo for next Monday."
}

### Schedule a follow-up
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/follow-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "delay_minutes": 30,
  "message_template": "Hi {{name}}, checking in on your enquiry."
}

### Escalate an enquiry
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/escalate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer asked for a human agent." 
}

### Get enquiry history
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/enquiry/1/history

### Health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
